videos.headline: Giannis turns rebound into an and-1

videos.description: The Suns pass the ball around before Jae Crowder caps off the possession with a 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Ball movement leads to Crowder's 3-pointer

videos.description: Khris Middleton drives by Cameron Payne for a layup while drawing contact.

videos.headline: Middleton gets by Payne for and-1

videos.description: P.J. Tucker passes to a driving Giannis Antetokounmpo, who finishes with a two-handed jam.

videos.headline: Tucker finds Giannis for thunderous dunk

videos.description: The Bucks display brilliant passing that ends with a Bobby Portis dunk and Giannis Antetokounmpo is loving it.

videos.headline: Giannis loves this sequence by the Bucks

videos.description: David Bakhtiari chugs a cup of beer at what seems to be light speed as he tries to get the Bucks fans hyped at Game 3 of the NBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NFL/NBA Misc. (David Bakhtiari and his dad fire up the crowd with their beer-chugging skills) 2021/07/11 ESHEET 3PV

videos.headline: David Bakhtiari and his dad fire up the crowd with their beer-chugging skills

videos.description: Cam Johnson gets a pass from Chris Paul, takes flight and elevates over P.J. Tucker for a ferocious dunk and foul.

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo gets the offensive rebound and fights through contact for the and-1 finish inside.

videos.description: Bucks fans erupt in celebration as Pat Connaughton knocks down a big 3-pointer to end the third quarter, giving Milwaukee a 98-76 lead.

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo scores 41 points with 13 rebounds and six assists as the Bucks take Game 3 from the Suns 120-100.
